ance and in other parts of the Continent."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Anna Maria Johnsdotter was born in 1421. She had at least 1 daughter with Samuel Samuelsson."},"et":{"1421–":"1421–Surnud","1415–1462":"1415–1462","1440–1513":"1440–1513","1421–Female":"1421–Surnud","1415":"1415","1513":"1513","1421":"1421","1440":"1440","1462":"1462","Linköping, Östergötland, Sweden":"Linköping, Östergötland, Rootsi"},"fi":{"1421–":"1421–Kuollut","1415–1462":"1415–1462","1440–1513":"1440–1513","1421–Female":"1421–Kuollut","1415":"1415","1513":"1513","1421":"1421","1440":"1440","1462":"1462","Linköping, Östergötland, Sweden":"Linköping, Östergötland, Ruotsi"},"fr":{"1421–":"1421–Décédée","1415–1462":"1415–1462","1440–1513":"1440–1513","1421–Female":"1421–Décédée","1415":"1415","1513":"1513","1421":"1421","1440":"1440","1462":"1462","Linköping, Östergötland, Sweden":"Linköping, Östergötland, Suède","lifeSummary":"Anna Maria Johnsdotter est née en 1421. Elle a eu au moins 1 fille avec Samuel Samuelsson."},"de":{"1421–":"1421–Verstorben","1415–1462":"1415–1462","1440–1513":"1440–1513","1421–Female":"1421–Verstorben","1415":"1415","1513":"1513","1421":"1421","1440":"1440","1462":"1462","Linköping, Östergötland, Sweden":"Linköping, Östergötland, Schweden","lifeSummary":"Anna Maria Johnsdotter wurde 1421 geboren. Sie hatte mit Samuel Samuelsson mindestens 1 Tochter."},"ht":{"1421–":"1421–Desede","1415–1462":"1415–1462","1440–1513":"1440–1513","1421–Female":"1421–Desede","1415":"1415","1513":"1513","1421":"1421","1440":"1440","1462":"1462","Linköping, Östergötland, Sweden":"Linköping, Östergötland, Suède"},"hu":{"1421–":"1421–elhunyt","1415–1462":"1415–1462","1440–1513":"1440–1513","1421–Female":"1421–elhunyt","1415":"1415","1513":"1513","1421":"1421","1440":"1440","1462":"1462","Linköping, Östergötland, Sweden":"Linköping, Östergötland, Svédország"},"id":{"1421–":"1421–Telah Meninggal","1415–1462":"1415–1462","1440–1513":"1440–1513","1421–Female":"1421–Telah Meninggal","1415":"1415